OL,3,GUK long range forecast
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Wed 15 Jul to Fri 24 Jul
OL,6,FHigh pressure to the northeast of the
OL,7,FUK with low pressure over the Bay of
OL,8,FBiscay starts the period with broadly
OL,9,Fsettled weather for the north of the
OL,10,FUK with a risk of thunderstorms into
OL,11,Fthe south of the UK from France at
OL,12,Ftimes. Through the weekend potentially
OL,13,Fturning more unsettled from the south
OL,14,Fbefore more settled conditions arrive
OL,15,Ffrom the west. Uncertain into the next
OL,16,Fweek as cloud and longer spells of
OL,17,Frain threaten the NW and possibly
OL,18,Frunning through the UK at times.
OL,19,FTemperatures will be warm or very warm
OL,20,Finitially, perhaps hot at times in the
OL,21,Fsouthwest, likely easing to warm or
OL,22,Fnear average over the weekend, though
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,23,Ffurther hot spells possible especially
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
OL,24,Fin the south..
