OL,3,GUK long range forecast
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Sat 25 Jul to Sat 8 AugFThe
OL,6,Fsignal through the end of July and
OL,7,Finto August becomes increasingly mixed
OL,8,Fwith spells of low pressure and more
OL,9,Funsettled weather becoming more
OL,10,Flikely. There may still be some
OL,11,Fthunderstorms at times as well. There
OL,12,Fwill still probably be some dry
OL,13,Finterludes, most probably in the south
OL,14,Fand southeast. Temperatures are likely
OL,15,Fto remain warm or very warm and some
OL,16,Fspells of hot weather remain possible.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
